\c 4
\s Kuidzwa kwaJesu.
\p (Mar. 1. 12-13; Ruka 4. 31-34.)
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jesu wakatungamirirwa noMweya kurenje kunoidzwa naDhiabhorosi.
\v 2 Wakati azvinyima zvokudya mazuva anamakumi mana novusiku makumi mana, akazova nenzara.
\v 3 Zvino muidzi wakati avuya kwaari, akati , kana uri Mwanakomana waMwari raira kuti mabwe awa aitwe zvingwa.
\v 4 Asi wakapindura akati, kwakanyorwa \add kuchinzi\add*, munhu haangararami nechingwa chete, asi neshoko rose rinobuda mumuromo maMwari.
\v 5 Zvino Dhiabhorosi akakwira naye muguta dzvene, akamuisa pachiruvu chetembere,
\v 6 akati kwaari, kana uri Mwanakomana waMwari, uzvikandire pasi, nokuti kwakanyorwa \add kuchinzi\add*, Iye ucharaira vatumwa vake pamusoro pako: pamavoko avo vachakutakura, kuti urege kugumbusa rutsoka rwako pabwe.
\v 7 Jesu akati kwaari, kwakanyorwavo, usaidza Ishe Mwari wako.
\v 8 Dhiabhorosi akamuisazve pagomo refusa, akamuratidza vushe bwose bwenyika, nokubwinya kwabwo.
\v 9 Akati kwaari, izvi zvose ndichapa kwauri kana ukawira pasi ukandimata.
\v 10 Ipapo Jesu akati kwaari, ibvapo Satani nokuti kwakanyorwa \add kuchinzi\add*: Uchamata Ishe Mwari wako, umushumire Iye woga.
\v 11 Zvino Dhiabhorosi akamurega. tarira vatumwa vakavuya vakamushumira.
\s Jesu paGariri. Vadzidzi vokutanga.
\p
\p
\v 12 Zvino Jesu wakati anzwa kuti Johwani wakandirwa \add mutirongo\add*, akaenda Gariri.
\v 13 Zvino wakabva Nazareta, akasvika akandogara muKapenaumi riri pamhenderekedzo dzegungwa, pamiganhu yeZebhuroni neNafitarimi,
\v 14 kuti zvizadzisike zvakarebwa naIsaya muporofita, achiti:
\v 15 Nyika yeZebhuroni nenyika yeNeftarimi, \add pa\add*nzira yegungwa, mhiri kwaJoridhani, Gariri ravahedheni.
\v 16 Vanhu vakanga vagere murima vakavona chiedza chikuru; Navakanga vagere panharaunda nomumvuri worufu, chiedza chakavabudira.
\v 17 Kubva panguva iyoyo Jesu wakatanga kuparidza, achiti: Tendevukai nokuti vushe bwokudenga bwaswedera.
\v 18 Zvino Jesu, \add wakati\add* achifamba pagungwa reGariri, akavona varume vaviri, \add vana vomunhu mumwe\add*, Simoni unonzi Petro naAndiriya munun'una wake vachikandira vutava mugungwa nokuti vakanga vari varedzi.
\v 19 Akati kwavari, Nditeverei, ndigokuitai varedzi vavanhu.
\v 20 Pakarepo vakasiya vutava \add bwavo\add* vakamutevera.
\v 21 Zvino wakati apfuvurira mberi akavona vamwe varume vaviri mugwa, \add vana\add* \add vomunhu mumwe\add*, Jakobho mwanakomana waZebhedhi naJohwani munun 'una wake vana Zebhedhi baba vavo, vachigadzira vutava bwavo, akavadana.
\v 22 Pakarepo vakasiya igwa nababa vavo vakamutevera.
\v 23 Jesu akapota neGariri rose achidzidzisa mumasinagoge avo. Achiparidza Evhangeri yovushe, achiporesa hosha dzamarudzi ose namarwere amarudzi ose pavanhu.
\v 24 Mukurumbira wake ukasvika kuSiria yose. Vakavuya kwaari navairwara vose, navakabatwa nehosha dzamarudzi mazhinji namarwadzo, navakanga vanemweya yakaipa, navanezvipusha, navakanga vakafa mitezo, akavaporesa.
\v 25 Vanhu vazhinji-zhinji vaibva Gariri neDhekapori, neJerusarema, neJudhiya, nemhiri kwaJoridhani vakamutevera.
